data.description: Amazing 2-Story home in Cumbre Vista. As you make your way inside, the beautiful colors and open space welcome you home. The home office is immediately off to your right to enjoy the convenience of having a true home office feeling. Venturing inside, you have an astounding kitchen which features all stainless steel appliances which include your range stove/oven, dishwasher, refrigerator, and microwave. The walk-out to the backyard is right off the dining area. Our living room is just adjacent from the kitchen, which has tons of natural light, great space, and a brick enclosed gas fireplace. Now heading upstairs is where we have all 3 of the featured bedrooms. Did I mention your laundry room is upstairs as well?? The master bedroom is voluminous with plenty of space for all your bedroom furniture and your large walk-in closet. Along with the bedrooms and bathrooms, this home has a sizable loft space. Enjoy a family room area, game room, second home office, or additional living space. Heading downstairs to the basement, we have our additional bedroom and bathroom, along with a commodious family room area. The second walk-out is located off the family room as well. Location is everything, just minutes away from shopping, restaurants, Powers Blvd & Mark Schuefful Road. This one won't last long, come see what all the fuss is about.
